originalSql:
SELECT 
    s.s_name AS supplier_name, 
    p.p_name AS part_name, 
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT c.c_mktsegment, ', ') AS market_segments,
    MIN(l.l_shipdate) AS first_ship_date,
    MAX(l.l_shipdate) AS last_ship_date
FROM 
    supplier s
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
WHERE 
    s.s_name LIKE '%Supplier%' 
    AND c.c_address LIKE '%Street%' 
    AND o.o_orderstatus = 'O' 
    AND l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1997-01-01' AND '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    s.s_name, p.p_name
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC
LIMIT 10

INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "part" ON "partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "s1"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "s1"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "orders"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
WHERE "supplier"."s_name" LIKE '%Supplier%' AND "customer"."c_address" LIKE '%Street%' AND "orders"."o_orderstatus" = 'O' AND "s1"."l_shipdate" >= '1997-01-01' AND "s1"."l_shipdate" <= '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_name", "part"."p_name"
ORDER BY 4 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t4"
